sentences: Ssewa Ssewa started playing music professionally in 2000.
He co-founded Janzi Band along with his friends in 2009 and has been the director since then.
He was one of the main performers at World Music Day in Uganda in June 2017 alongside Apio Moro, Haka Mukiga, Mame Ndiak, Jackie Akello and many others.
